title: F.T.C. Sues Amazon for Inducing Users to Subscribe to Prime
description: The lawsuit was the first time that the Federal Trade Commission under chair Lina Khan has taken Amazon to court.

title: Dolby Atmos Wants You to Listen Up. (And Down. And Sideways.)
